    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it seriously looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. If you\u2019re looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
