    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable example of the A80 chassis, this Supra Turbo retains its original 2JZ-GTE inline-six powerplant, featuring the factory-correct sequential twin-turbocharging system. Power is delivered through the legendary Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The vehicle exhibits zero chassis flex, with all factory spot welds and VIN tags intact. Every bushing remains compliant, and the double-wishbone suspension maintains its original geometry. The engine bay is a testament to preservation, showing no heat cycling fatigue on the wiring harness or vacuum lines. Compression across all cylinders is within factory-spec tolerances. This is a true survivor, free of any aftermarket modifications, preserving the intended aerodynamic balance and mechanical harmony of this JDM icon.",
